high_descs: go to the countertop in the kitchen.
take the knife from the top of the countertop.
Slice the potato on the counter.
turn around and walk through the hallway to get to the room with the potato.
Put the knife down on the dresser.
turn around and walk pass the dresser to get to the kitchen.
walk to the countertop, where the cut potatoes are.
pick up a slice of the potato.
go to the diningtable.
Put the slice of potato away from the diningtable.
turn around and go to the countertop again.
pick up another piece of potato
walk to the diningtable with the microwave.

anns.task_desc: Get a potato, slice it, and take it to the dining table.

high_descs: Turn left and go across to the countertop in the kitchen.
Pick up the knife on the counter between the plate and frying pan.
Slice the potato near the back of the plate.
Slice the potato on the left side.
Turn right, go to the doorway and go across to the dresser.
Place the knife on the dresser to the left of the credit card.
Head back to the countertop in the kitchen.
Pick up a slice of the potato on the right.
Turn around to the diningtable.
Place the potato on the diningtable near the microwave.
Head back to the potato on the countertop.
Pick up a slice of the potato on the left.
Head back to the diningtable.
Place the potato slice on the diningtable in front of the microwave to the right.
anns.task_desc: Place two slices of Potato on the DiningTable in front of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go into the hall, turning left towards the countertop ahead.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the potato farthest on the plate.
Slice the closer potato on the plate.
Turn around and go straight, then right into the next room, heading towards the dresser in the corner.
Place the knife down on the dresser.
Head back to the sliced potatoes on the countertop.
Pick up one slice of potato from the far potato.
Turn around and walk forward stopping at the diningtable on the right.
Place the potato slice on the diningtable with the microwave.
Return to the potato slices on the countertop.
Pick up a potato slice from the other potato.
Return to the diningtable.
Place the second potato slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Slice two Potatoes and place one slice from each on a DiningTable.
